SOR clip.notes: Can delay time of day to make Blood Moon timing better. Options are (1) right now, (2) after paraglider, (3) after rupee printer, or (4) after Medoh.

_Material<Food>.notes: DON'T eat baked apple (quest), stamella (transmute in Tarrey Town), and keep peppers x6 (transmute in Kakariko)

.dir(BLSS).notes: WB <E turn to opening cutscene if delaying time of day until now.

.loc(Hyrule Castle balcony).notes: Can try to discover Observation Room now but you can die if the malice spawns.

.!!(Select Magnesis, SAVE).notes: Ideal combos are shaft+part or core+part. Shaft+screw and shaft+spring combos do not give enough rupees so you'll need to take elite pictures.

Kill guardian.notes: Every core you get lets you skip a shrine chest; need 15 springs before Akkala Tech Lab

_Korok::C30.notes: Trigger and cancel a controller swap to be able to safely warp away.

.dir(BLSS).notes: WB <E turn to opening cutscene if delaying time of day until now.

_Korok::R60.notes: Kill the birds here for extra food.

_Shop<Shop>.notes: Drop 5 cores and sell rest OR sell all gears OR sell 600 shafts

_Equipment::Bow<Arrows x10>.notes: Ignore Swallow Bow, not enough inventory space for it

_Material<Cold Darner,2>.notes: For An Ice Guy quest and Little Sister's Big Request. Backup on the bridge to Akh Va'quot or near Rito Stable.

_Npc<Beedle>.notes: Talk twice so that you get the "customer appreciation" ancient arrow. Darner is for Little Sister's Big Request. Fireflies are for transmuting.

_Material<Voltfin>.notes: If you don't get a voltfin, reload.

.dir(BLSS).notes: WB <E turn to opening cutscene if delaying time of day until now.

_Shop<Produce Shop>.notes: Carrots/gut for speed food, eggs for transmuting.

Activate Ta'loh Naeg.notes: Slightly faster to complete later with speed food.

.!!(Camera and slate upgrades).notes: 3 shafts for bombs+; 3 screws for sensor+; 3 cores for stasis+.

_Korok::F26.notes: Beetles despawn at 7am, skip this if it's getting late.

_Material<Fleet Lotus Seed,30>.notes: If guardian sees you, use Cryo and head shots to buy time.

_Equipment::Bow<3 Duplex Bow>.notes: Duplex Bows needed for menu overload and for Weapon Connoisseur.

Activate Daqo Chisay.notes: Slightly faster to do it later with speed food.

_Tod::Morning.notes: For ice house time of day.

_Npc<Bozai>.notes: Eighth Heroine and Forgotten Sword quests

_Korok::W46.notes: Break damaged pot lid here to clear inventory.

Begin free Naydra.notes: Shoot an eye before each of the following koroks

_Korok::N30.notes: Stasis and bomb from a distance

_Shop<General Store>.notes: Sizzlefin and chillfin used for transmuting.

_Npc::Goron<Greyson>.notes: Make night if needed to speak to him.

_Shrine::KetohWawai.notes: Need 2 cores for Ancient Short Sword.

.enemy(Kill White-Maned Lynel).notes: Hoof is for Riddles of Hyrule. Lynel Crusher is just nice to have for 1 hinox.

_Shrine::GoraeTorr.notes: Wb E and then midair W.

_Korok::A15.notes: If you have 14 springs, you can dumpster dive here for 15.

_Npc<Cherry>.notes: Sword for Weapon Connoisseur. If missing parts, warp back later.

_Tod::Night.notes: Also helps blood moon timing. If blood moon happens now, it can be canceled by being inside Tutsuwa Nima.

_Boss::Talus::Igneo.notes: Check for 10 luminous stones, collect gems.

_Npc<Tasho>.notes: Move forward until you hear Oaki's dialogue to trigger the escort.

_Npc<Walton>.notes: Apple, pumpkin, sunshroom, voltfin, lynel hoof.

_Tod::Night.notes: Cancels blood moon by forcing it to occur while you're in Hyrule Castle.

_Chest<Star Fragment>.notes: Need 3 star fragments for quests. The other 2 come from quest rewards.

_Equipment::Weapon<Blizzard Rod>.notes: Completes the Freezing Rod quest and also good for lizalfos fights and knocking down rushrooms.

Hyrule Castle: Hit switch to turn on updraft

.!!(Dupe/Transfer/Transmute).notes: .link([Example]https://youtu.be/gQH8hwsckaM?t=24487). Blood moon will happen during this. That's ok.

.code(Round 2a).notes: These are +1 dupes except for Farosh's Scale (+2)

.code(Round 2b).notes: If missing any parts, can always sell guardian parts instead.

_Material<Apple,2>.notes: You have no apples after transmuting and offering koroks are coming up.

_Material<Molduga Gut>.notes: Picking up all parts here makes buying enough mon from Kilton later very safe.

_Npc<Bozai>.notes: Eighth Heroine and Forgotten Sword quests

_Tod::Night.notes: For Xenoblade chest when you get to Bridge of Hylia.

Ride horse.notes: Set up the horse for easy pickup later.

_Korok::L65.notes: Do not whistle sprint until after Shoqa Tatone.

_Korok::D31.notes: Midair strat only if not raining.

_Equipment::Weapon<Traveler's Sword>.notes: Need to get here before 5am. Backup in Kakariko later.

_Boss::Hinox::Red.notes: If you skipped F26 after Farosh, E> to get it now.

_Chest<Sapphire>.notes: Sunken Treasure quest. Only need to open 1 chest.

_Npc<Rozel>.notes: Inside house under F44 if raining. Sunken Treasure quest

_Tod::Night.notes: For upcoming stalnox. Might not be needed.
For a stalnox on Satori Mountain.

.dir(N> + climb).notes: Optionally use gale 1 here if recharged.

Start T06 race.notes: If you make a mistake, you can finish T06 right after H60. Then do H60 to T07.

_Boss::Hinox::Blue.notes: Smuggle an arrow by shooting with a single shot bow.

_Tod::Night.notes: There are 2 Energetic Rhino Beetles, one at each gate, for backup

_Shop<Armor Shop>.notes: Sell guardian parts last to trigger compendium glitch.

.!!(Upgrade all armor).notes: Set of the Wild, Zora Set, Champion's Tunic

_Npc<Hudson>.notes: Talk to him again after the wedding.

_Npc<Hestu>.notes: Talk to him again for the poop!
